			<div><strong>Spell Refresh Bar (Drakah)</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>Howdy again!!!<br />
     I am using Drakah's Mod where you have the spell cast timer bar in the player info window. What I am wondering is if there is a way to have the same bar when you cast a spell and it drains down to zero....have it also correspond to the time you are able to recast. What I mean is the only way you know if you can recast is when your Spell Gem bar starts to appear again. To me it's kinda a pain. It would be nice to have the bar that counts down your cast time also count up the bar to time you are able to cast again. When it's full again you know you can recast. Is that possible? I didn't see any EQtype for that but didn't look very hard for one. Even if I found one I am not InTeLiJeNt enuf to add it myself ). If it's possible and can be done...would someone mind doing that modding the casting bar to do that in Drakah's or at least post the XML text you would need to add to be able to do it.<br />
<br />
Thanks in advance<br />
Chad</div>
